<% content_for(:title) { "Privacy Policy - Cambodia Postal Code Directory" } %>

<div class="legal-page">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: <%= Date.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>Cambodia Postal Code Directory ("we", "our", or "the Service") is a free tool for looking up Cambodian postal codes. We are committed to protecting your privacy and being transparent about our data practices.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3>Usage Statistics</h3>
    <p>We collect anonymous, aggregated statistics to understand how the Service is used:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Visit counts</strong> - Total number of page visits</li>
      <li><strong>Search counts</strong> - Total number of searches performed</li>
      <li><strong>Copy counts</strong> - Total number of postal codes copied</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These statistics are anonymous counters and cannot be linked to individual users.</p>

    <h3>Location Data</h3>
    <p>If you use the "Find My Location" feature:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your browser will ask for permission before sharing location data</li>
      <li>GPS coordinates are sent to our server to find nearby postal codes</li>
      <li>Location data may be cached temporarily to improve performance</li>
      <li>We do not store or track your location history</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Analytics</h3>
    <p>We use Google Analytics to understand traffic patterns and improve the Service. Google Analytics may collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
      <li>Device type and browser information</li>
      <li>Approximate geographic location (country/city level)</li>
      <li>Referring websites</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For more information, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Information We Do NOT Collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Personal identification information (name, email, phone)</li>
      <li>User accounts or login credentials</li>
      <li>Search history linked to individuals</li>
      <li>Cookies for tracking individual users (beyond analytics)</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>The limited data we collect is used to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Display aggregate usage statistics on the website</li>
      <li>Improve the Service based on usage patterns</li>
      <li>Ensure the Service is working correctly</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or share your information with third parties, except:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Google Analytics (as described above)</li>
      <li>When required by law</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Your Choices</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Location:</strong> You can deny location permission in your browser</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> You can use browser extensions to opt out of Google Analytics</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through <a href="https://gotabs.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gotabs Consulting</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <p class="back-link"><a href="/">Back to Search</a></p>
</div>
